65786190711594?refer=embed&quot;>;♬ 原声 - The Verge&lt;/a>; &lt;/section>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;i7SkMm&quot;>;如果您无法观看该视频，没关系。我也...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24176837/apple-ios-18-macos-sequoia-beta-updates-wwdc-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24176837/apple-ios-18-macos-sequoia-beta-updates-wwdc-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24176837/apple-ios-18-macos-sequoia-beta-updates-wwdc-2024</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-12T12:22:47-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-12T12:22:47-04:00</updated><title> Epic Games 数据库泄露暗示存在大量未发布的游戏</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Epic Games 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ex9DzlaB9L578hwmr2Th4kQl8_w=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/ image/73403317/acastro_STK108__01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;PyDCCy&quot;>;跟踪 Epic Games 库中游戏的非官方网站可能有正如之前报道的那样，刚刚泄露了大量即将推出的游戏 &lt;a href=&quot;https://wccftech.com/major-epic-leak-hints-at-unannounced-games-coming-to-epic-games-store/&quot;>;由 &lt;em>;Wccftech&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 提供。该网站名为 EpicDB，在周一发布从 Epic Games Store 目录中抓取的信息后不久就被下线，但这并没有阻止人们扫描列表并发布他们的发现。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;mDSrAT &quot;>;您可以在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.resetera.com/threads/a- 发布的一系列屏幕截图中看到 Bethesda、Sega、Sony、Square Enix 等发行商的游戏列表。很多-unannounced-games-are-leaking-via-epicdb.898755/&quot;>;ResetEra 论坛上的用户&lt;/a>;。虽然有些（例如 Turok）很容易发现，但其他一些则以之前传闻的代号列出，例如 &lt;a href=&quot;https://kotaku.com/sources-the-new-bioshock-has -been-in-the-works-for-yea-1840314561&quot;>;“Parkside&lt;em>;”&lt;/em>;或&lt;em>;生化奇兵 4&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;EVW2yT&quot;>;还有其他代号的游戏我们还没有听说过。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.reddit.com/r/GamingLeaksAndRumours/comments/1ddua4x/epicdb_several_publisher_games_are_being_leaked/?share_id=6m1QV-LYimeoJ1TcX40o5&amp;amp;utm_content=1&amp;amp;utm_medium=android_app&amp;amp;utm_name=androidcss&amp;amp;utm_source=分享&amp;utm_term= 1&quot;>;一些用户推测&lt;/a>;“Momo”...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/12/24176964/epic-games -database-leak-unannounced-games&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/12/24176964/epic-games-database-leak-unannounced-games" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/12/24176964/epic-games-database-leak-unannounced-games</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-12T12:13:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-12T12:13:30-04:00</updated><title> Life360 确认黑客窃取了 Tile 跟踪器 ID 和客户信息</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;手拿着一个黑色方形瓷砖追踪器，上面有一张棕色木桌，上面有一棵多肉植物。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/YA9hXbNB4iBxke8zKOQo0Nq8rDI=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73403301/ajohnson_210702_4659_0002。 0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;照片由 Allison Johnson / The Verge 拍摄&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UzOt1x&quot;>;黑客入侵了 Tile 设备跟踪器背后的系统并窃取了客户数据，包括姓名、地址、电子邮件和电话号码。根据&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.404media.co/hacker-accesses-internal-tile-tool-that-provides-location-data-to-cops/&quot;>;404 Media 的报道&lt;/ em>;&lt;/a>;，黑客能够通过访问用于响应有关 Tile 跟踪器的执法请求的工具来收集客户信息。被盗信息不包括精确的 Tile 位置数据。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;EGxE86&quot;>;Life360，拥有 Tile，&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs= 1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tile.com%2Fen-us%2Fblog%2Funauthorized-access-incident-2024&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com% 2F2024%2F6%2F12%2F24176889%2Ftile-life360-customer-data-breach-hacker-extortion&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;发布了首席执行官 Chris Hulls 的声明&lt;/a>;，承认此次黑客攻击。 Hulls 证实这些数据包括 Tile 跟踪器 ID，并表示黑客曾试图勒索 Life360，该公司已向执法部门报告了此事。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;wr0pq2&quot;>;在给 &lt;em>;The Verge 的电子邮件中&lt; /em>;，赫尔斯写道，“据我所知，几乎没有被访问过。”赫尔斯没有回应...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/12/24176889/tile-life360-customer-data-breach-hacker-extortion &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/12/24176889/tile-life360-customer-data-breach-hacker-extortion" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/12/24176889/tile-life360-customer-data-breach-hacker-extortion</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-12T12:00:03-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-12T12:00:03-04:00</updated><title> Jabra 的耳塞式耳机即将消失，但它们所产生的影响却并未消失</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/IwfluAspYzXiQwZ-feHk4y1sa2Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /73403285/akrales_180411_2462_0082.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;该公司的 Elite 耳塞恰逢其时，并获得了辉煌的时刻，但最终还是结束了这是不可避免的。感谢 Jabra 推动多点技术直至成为常态。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24176836/jabra-earbuds-retrospective-65t-75t-apple-sony&quot; >;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24176836/jabra-earbuds-retrospective-65t-75t-apple-sony" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24176836/jabra-earbuds-retrospective-65t-75t-apple-sony</id><author><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-12T11:58:40-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-12T11:58:40-04:00</updated><title>华纳兄弟正在通过更多《探险活宝》来加强其动画阵容</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《冒险时光》中的角色在绿草如茵的山丘上嬉戏。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/9OqoB6rQYAjOnSHz8_TnBRGv6CM=/94x0:1107x675/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73403253/adventuretime5.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：卡通网络&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;